  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This, this doubt has permeated the general [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] populace.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And although the majority, the nontraditional Hungarians, who were themselves badly informed and subject to this, this misleading propaganda, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and of course, being wishful human beings themselves, they were all hoping that some miracle will happen.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By that time, the Germans started to send the the V-2s, to London.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was a lot of rumors circulating about the, the miracle weapons what the Germans are now developing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So essentially they have been all hoping that these miracle weapons will, in, in this late stage, still work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "However, the official attitude showed a, a definite sign of appeasement.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had the prime minister for a short time, who was Lakatos.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was the, the epitome of this-- of this realization that the war is lost.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it's futile to, to, to, to, to, to, to fight.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it's completely counterproductive to kill these 200,000 Jews now left in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- I had an uncle-- I had relatives in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had-- I had my, my auntie, my uncle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had another uncle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I had quite a lot of people in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My uncle, who was the black sheep of the family, who didn't want to be a lawyer, but became a baker-- remember I told you about him?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a baker and a very clever man, very unusual man, who somehow-- I don't know how-- got some exception-- exemption for himself, right, based on his heroism during the First World War, all of which only, only 25% was true.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he got that.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
